  "prompt": "Read jobs.json which describes a flexible job-shop scheduling problem. There are 3 machines (0,1,2) and 3 jobs, each with 3 operations. Each operation lists which machines can process it and the duration on each machine. Operations within a job must be processed in order (precedence). Each machine can process only one operation at a time. Some machines have scheduled downtime windows. Find a feasible schedule that minimizes makespan. Write results to schedule.json with keys: assignments (array of objects with op_id, machine, start, end), makespan (number).",
